data.description: Downtown, Renovated Beachside multi-family only TWO BLOCKS from the beach! Property is generating $5,850 per month gross. This multi-family residence has had 3 of its 4 units renovated and is fully leased out at 100% occupancy. Along with freshly painted interiors, the renovated units include a series of upgrades including new laminate floors and restored hardwood floors. Those unit's bathrooms feature new showers, tubs, vanities, and toilets. The kitchens have been upgraded with new white shaker cabinetry and stainless-steel appliances, which is complimented by the granite countertops and backsplash. Newer metal roof and 7 new windows.
